encrypt - File Encryption/Decryption

USAGE:
    encrypt -target=<file> [-r=<recipients>] [-t]

DESCRIPTION:
    Encrypt or decrypt files using GPG.

OPTIONS:
    -target=<file>
        File to encrypt/decrypt (required)

    -r=<recipients>
        Recipients for encryption

    -t
        Sign and armor data

EXAMPLES:
    encrypt -target=document.pdf
    encrypt -target=secret.txt -r=user@example.com
    encrypt -target=data.zip -r=user1@example.com,user2@example.com -t
